<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="push-v">push <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pʊʃ/    美 /pʊʃ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-pull-press">1.★ <strong>推 (动) 【反:pull】；按下 (press)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>pushed</strong> the door <strong>open</strong> and showed the doctor in.
她推开门把大夫领了进来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>pushed</strong> her hair <strong>back</strong> from her forehead.
她把头发从前额往后拨。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>push the button
按下按钮</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>挤；推挤：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>pushed through</strong> the crowd.
我们从人群中挤过。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>pushed their way into</strong> the train looking for seats.
他们挤上火车寻找座位。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>劝说；鼓励：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>push sb into (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My teacher pushed me into entering the competition.
我的老师鼓励我参加比赛。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>逼迫；催促：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Athletes <strong>push</strong> themselves <strong>to the extreme limit</strong> of their body to complete the over 42 kilometers race.
要完成超过42公里的赛程，运动员需要把自己的体能发挥到极限。</p><footer>2008 广东</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Set your alarm clock an hour early and push yourself to work out!
把你的闹钟调前一小时，强迫自己去锻炼。</p><footer>2018 全国</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="push-aside">push aside</h3>
<p>1.<strong>推开；排挤；设法忘掉：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Just when she was about to speak, a student rushed in and pushed her aside!
正当她要讲话时，一个学生冲了进来将她推到一边。</p><footer>2015 广东</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She pushed aside her anger, forcing herself to focus on her work. 
她抛开愤怒，强迫自己专心工作。</p></div>

<h3 id="push-on">push on</h3>
<p>1.<strong>继续前进；继续 (做某事)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let’s push on; it’s nearly nightfall.
咱们继续走吧，天快黑了。</p></div>

<h3 id="push-over">push over</h3>
<p>1.<strong>推倒；(风) 刮倒：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The big tree was pushed over by the wind. 
这棵大树被风刮倒了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Encourage your children to try new things, but try not to <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (逼迫) them too hard.  （2009 全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. push  </p></div>